[Extended] Design Your Story Season 5


04 Jul 2025

[Extended] Design Your Story Season 5




4th July 2025 ~ 31st August 2025, 2359hrs 30th September 2025, 2359hrs

Design Your Story has returned after 4 years!

Maplers, it's time to unleash your creativity! Submit your dream Cash Shop outfit for a chance to see it in the game. This season has no specific theme, so let your imagination run wild!


Submission Guidelines:
1. Include your MapleID, IGN, and World in your artwork.
2. Designs can be digital or scanned images (no text-only submissions).
3. Your design must be a cash equipment outfit set. You may also include hair, face, pets , rings or chair designs together with the Cash Outfit design.
4. Absolutely no AI-generated art is allowed.

Important Note:
  • Once your design is ready, send your submissions in an email to the designated email address (designyourstory@playpark.com) with the subject "Design Your Story Season 5 - Submission by [[MapleID]]".
  • Multiple submissions should be separated and sent with separated individual e-mail submission.
  • Please include your Maple ID, IGN, and World in your e-mail. We may disqualify incomplete submissions.
  • For Example: Design Your Story Season 5 - Submission by mymapleid123
  • Up to 5 submissions allowed per MapleID, and recommended to have a short write-up about the concept to better illustrate the rationale.
  • Maple Team will review all eligible designs, and only the top entry will be implemented into the game.
